To list all the S3 Buckets 
 aws s3 ls 

To list particular bucket 
 aws s3 ls s3://bucketname

To create a S3 bucket 
 aws s3 mb s3://uniquename

To Upload a file from EC2 to S3 (Put Object)
 aws s3 cp sourcefile S3://bucketname

To Download a file from S3 to EC2 (Get Object)
 aws s3 cp s3://bucketname/filename Destination_path

To Download all files from S3 to EC2
 aws s3 sync s3://bucketname Destination_Path

To remove a file in S3 bucket
 aws s3 rm s3://bucketname/filename

